282
00:28:44.250 --> 00:28:45.250
What are you doing?

283
00:28:45.500 --> 00:28:46.708
Don't you see it?

284
00:28:47.500 --> 00:28:48.667
You invited Alice.

285
00:28:49.125 --> 00:28:50.792
She was Will's wife.

286
